    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The program has been completed\nfor the annual convention of the\nSpokane county w. C. T. u,\nwhich will convene in Lidgerwood\nCongregational church, Gordon and\nStandard, June 17-1S. Three busy\nsessions each day are laid out, the\nmorning beginning at 9. afternoon\nat 1870 and evening at 8. Reports\non the various branches of the\nwoman's temperance work will be\nsubmitted by the proper officers\nand a program of special features\nand addresses is provided.\n\n\nThe executive committee meets\nbefore the convention opens Friday\nmorning and officers will be elect\ned Friday forenoon."
    }
  ]
